On Thu, 11 Jul 2002, Richard Atwell wrote:

> I just got a CV boot kit from BusDepot.  It's Meistersatz and I'm wondering
> how it seals to the axle.
>
> http://img.eautopartscatalog.com/hires/K601018706FEB.JPG
> http://img.eautopartscatalog.com/hires/K601018706LOB.JPG
>
> This is an image of the Febi and Lobro kits and they both have two extra
> clips for the end of the boot.
>
> Why is my kit missing these two pieces?

My Meisterwhatever kits had the little crimp clamps.  Unfortunately the
boots didn't last all that long once on.  I think that quality varies
widely.

A lot of folks don't use clamps on the axle end.  I've never seen this
part of the boot leak at all, clamps or no.

